decide who was right.

00:12:55.790 --> 00:12:58.840
Whether the school board, the
people from the schools were right,

00:12:58.840 --> 00:13:01.650
or whether the families,
like the Mendez family

00:13:01.650 --> 00:13:04.580
and the other families involved
